Detailed Description

cvmx_mix::_orhwm

MIX_ORHWM = MIX O-Ring High-Water Mark Threshold Register

Description: NOTE: To write to the MIX_ORHWM register, a device would issue an IOBST directed at the MIO. To read the MIX_ORHWM register, a device would issue an IOBLD64 directed at the MIO.
